{"tid":600662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[廢老Vs]沙田瀝源兩躁翁打架　67歲翁送院亡　七旬疑兇逃去","createTime":"2018-03-21T13:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T15:21:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"33d094b3cee708f30afd32e63be36fb13a3163f0","tid":600662,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"沙田瀝源邨發生打架傷人案，一名男子昏迷送院，經搶救後證實不治。另一人仍然在逃<br />\n<br />\n下午3時25分，警方接報於瀝源邨華豐樓，兩名老翁於地下一間教會門外打架，其中一名67歲姓吳男子當場頭破血流，受傷昏迷，救護員到場將傷者送院搶救。現場消息指，兩人並不相識，卻因瑣事發生口角，繼而互相揮拳襲擊，另一名年約60至70歲的男子傷人後逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，經初步調查，案件一度列「在公眾地方打架」，案件交由沙田警區重案組跟進，暫未有人被捕。現時警方將案件改列謀殺案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/170493/-%E6%8B%B3%E9%A0%AD%E4%BA%A4%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%80%9D%E6%BA%90%E5%85%A9%E8%BA%81%E7%BF%81%E6%89%93%E6%9E%B6-67%E6%AD%B2%E7%BF%81%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%BA%A1-%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E7%96%91%E5%85%87%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F170493%2F-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%2580%259D%25E6%25BA%2590%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25BA%2581%25E7%25BF%2581%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%259E%25B6-67%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2597%25AC%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%2587%25E9%2580%2583%25E5%258E%25BB&d=%2FDtg%2F59PK1glyPu4UB1EgTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9b08d1e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/170493/-%E6%8B%B3%E9%A0%AD%E4%BA%A4%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%80%9D%E6%BA%90%E5%85%A9%E8%BA%81%E7%BF%81%E6%89%93%E6%9E%B6-67%E6%AD%B2%E7%BF%81%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%BA%A1-%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E7%96%91%E5%85%87%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB</a>"},{"pid":"7520fb4ad6930aa9888291d7797d5c438828cf94","tid":600662,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size